{
  "stem": "17.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 206.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] again, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] with all these atrocities, the fact that we-- we-- we didn't know the truth helped us survive our own life, and trying to-- to protect ourself, to be able to be with the families, together.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Did you believe--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After my mother left, I was devastated for a couple days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It-- it was this instinctive feeling, even that I was reassured that she will live, she will survive.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the fact that we were separated, it was very hard to-- to accept.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember, I was staying in bed for couple days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't want to eat or do anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But again, the life comes back to you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's a-- it's a strong instinct with-- with young people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I guess we got back into some activities.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't remember if we worked at that time, or-- or taking these courses.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But anyway, we started to be active again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then, of course, this [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] life was deteriorating.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There were more often selections, and-- and at, unexpectedly, at different time of the days.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there were more people coming to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There were some taken to the concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And was tremendous influx of-- of people from-- from other towns or other countries.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Rather, rather from Poland.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Mostly from Poland and from Germany.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So that was this constant movement of people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There were some disposed of, and here you have a wave of new ones again.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And just to-- to-- to live in this atmosphere, it's-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was hard to maintain-- this what you were.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "This what you were trained as a child to be.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But again, that was hope and survival.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
